data.description: Situated in the vibrant community of Mont Belvieu, TX, this two-story home beckons with its spacious layout and convenient location. Boasting five bedrooms, it offers ample space for growing household or hosting guests. The main floor features a luxurious primary bedroom. Step into the heart of the home, where an open-concept living area seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living spaces, ideal for entertaining. Outside, a custom covered patio awaits in the backyard, providing a serene retreat for outdoor gatherings or peaceful relaxation. In the evening, the exterior lighting enhances the beauty of the home. Extras such as a whole house water system with reverse osmosis at kitchen sink, wiring for a generator, security cameras front and back add to the value of the home. Easy access to a plethora of restaurants and local businesses. With its blend of functionality and charm, this gem is ready to welcome new owners into a life of comfort and convenience.
